{"tid":695970,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"著對新鞋入公廁屙尿畀廢老d尿滴濕咗","createTime":"2018-06-09T16:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T03:08:49.000Z","uid":170044,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b8aae188c90638ce908fa0346b81fa7595991a70","tid":695970,"uid":170044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T16:04:25.000Z","msg":"前幾日買咗對新鞋 白色的<br />\n今日出街點都要新鞋落地 見下人<br />\n出出下街急尿 就入咗附近公廁屙尿<br />\n一入到去 見到好多尿斗底下都係濕<br />\n唔知係尿定水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過唔理了<br />\n搵到個啱位就屙<br />\n點個屙屙下個有個廢老特登黎咗我格黎到屙<br />\n佢仲要一路屙尿一直想望住我條J<br />\n咁我緊係用手遮一遮啦<br />\n點知佢條仆街仲要滴d尿落我對新鞋到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74410195f3fc14115d9338e1604339c42c88b338","tid":695970,"uid":158585,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T16:07:54.000Z","msg":"屙番尿落佢隻涼鞋到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdfcdad8e6ba9200cba939add487d120c23b6357","tid":695970,"uid":5649,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T16:09:59.000Z","msg":"阿伯 你個尿兜係果到呀"},{"pid":"ef42308dfb7bf714b940a958007a5d988b2862fa","tid":695970,"uid":91878,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T16:11:19.000Z","msg":"冇喇？"},{"pid":"96b89433a3944185af8fcb62d85a76e58f798ad6","tid":695970,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T16:12:10.000Z","msg":"下次含住佢條撚"},{"pid":"2fa534472fdd2a64ded31fc774fc7526e0214e4e","tid":695970,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T16:12:52.000Z","msg":"個呀伯啱啱起公園打完飛機尿急入公廁屙尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而家樓主對鞋上面黏住個雞蟲呀伯嘅精液同尿液，快啲掉撚咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5466c0218879a3a965afbfe5ff933ef561a166fb","tid":695970,"uid":187513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T16:16:12.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"8546e77